<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٦١:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {فَمَا لَهُمْ عَنِ التَّذْكِرَةِ مُعْرِضِينَ <span class="c2">(٤٩)</span> كَأَنَّهُمْ حُمُرٌ مُسْتَنْفِرَةٌ <span class="c2">(٥٠)</span> فَرَّتْ مِنْ قَسْوَرَةٍ <span class="c2">(٥١)</span>} <span class="c4">[المدثر: ٤٩ - ٥١]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{مُسْتَنْفِرَةٌ}</span>: <span class="c2">«نَافِرَةٌ مَذْعُورَةٌ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{قَسْوَرَةٌ}</span>: <span class="c2">«رِكْزُ النَّاسِ وَأَصْوَاتُهُمْ، وَكُلُّ شَدِيدٍ قَسْوَرَةٌ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ أَبُو هُرَيْرَةَ:</span> القَسْوَرَةُ: <span class="c1">" قَسْوَرٌ الأَسَدُ،<span class="c5"> الرِّكْزُ:</span> الصَّوْتُ "</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>